    "content": "Tabbed by: bassm99\r\nE-mail: alanmatthews1966@yahoo.co.uk\r\n\r\nTuning: E, A, D, G\r\n\r\n\"Angel\" from the album \"Like A Virgin\" (1984)\r\nWritten by Madonna/Steve Bray\r\n\r\nBass Starts: 0:15\r\n\r\nIntro: \r\n \r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--3-3-3-3-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nVerse: (Play 8 Times)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--0-0-0-0--2-2-2-2--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3---------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nChorus (Play 4 Times)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--0-0-0-0--2-2-2-2--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3---------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Verse:\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus: (Play 8 Times)\r\n\r\nBridge: (Play Twice)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--0-0-2-3-3-3-3-3--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3--0-0-2-3-3-3-3-3--2-2-2-2-2-2-2-2------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus: (Play 4 Times)\r\n\r\nRepeat Verse: (Play 4 Times)\r\n\r\nRepeat Chorus: (Play 12 Times)\r\n\r\nEnding: (Play 9 Times To Fade)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|--0-0-0-0--2-2-2-2--3-3-3-3-3-3-3-3---------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]",
